[
  "Charles Dunstone is chairman of TalkTalk Telecom and former chairman of electronics retailer Dixons Carphone, both based in the UK.",
  "In 1989, Dunstone started Carphone Warehouse in his apartment with $12,000 in savings. In 2014, Carphone merged with Dixons, an electronics retailer. ",
  "The move was seen as a bet on the growth of the Internet of Things, the increasing web-connectivity of home appliances and electronics.",
  "He also founded TalkTalk, a spin-off from Carphone Warehouse, in 2002."
]